title: Three Palestinian Students Shot and Injured  Near University of Vermont, Say Police
description: Three young men of Palestinian descent were shot near the University of Vermont. Authorities said the attack may have been a hate crime.

title: Biden Says Four-Year-Old American Girl Is Among Hostages Released From Gaza
description: Abigail Edan was among the 17 hostages freed by Hamas on Sunday.

title: Curfew Set in Sierra Leone After Gunmen Attack Military Barracks and Detention Centers
description: Sierra Leone’s president declared a nationwide curfew after gunmen attacked the military's main barracks and overran detention centers.

title: Irish-Israeli Hostage Emily Hand, 9, Is Reunited With Her Father After Release
description: Schoolgirl Emily Hand was among the second group of hostages to be released by Hamas.

title: Accenture’s Chief AI Officer Lan Guan on Why This Is a Defining Moment
description: Accenture's chief AI officer Lan Guan says there is a lot of work to do to make sure AI is democratized.
